    "title": "Lead Revenue Manager at Swiggy Restaurant Partners",
    "description": "We at Swiggy Restaurant Partners are looking for an experienced Revenue Manager based out of Pune. If you are a result-oriented professional with a passion for excellence, we want to hear from you.\n\nAbout Swiggy Restaurant Partners:\nSwiggy Restaurant Partners is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Plan and execute banquets, events, and MICE functions\n• Develop and maintain relationships with corporate clients\n• Assist in menu planning, costing, and food festival coordination\n• Manage front office operations including check-in/check-out\n• Deliver exceptional guest experiences in line with brand standards\n• Coordinate housekeeping and maintenance for room readiness\n• Train and supervise front-line staff on service standards\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• MBA from a recognized university\n• 0-1 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Front Office\n• Proficiency in Hotel Management\n• Proficiency in Travel Management\n• Proficiency in HACCP\n• Proficiency in Opera PMS\n• Proficiency in Barista Skills\n• Proficiency in Revenue Management\n• Proficiency in GDS Systems\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Flexible working hours\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Salary Range: 2.5 LPA - 6 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Pune, Maharashtra, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Swiggy Restaurant Partners!",
